	</tr>

  	<tr>
		<td width="94" valign="top" align="left"><a href="/wgbh/nova/thin/"><img src="/wgbh/nova/images02/icon_2715_thin.jpg" alt="Dying to be Thin" width="80" height="61" border="0" hspace="0" vspace="0" /></a></td>
		<td valign="top"><p class="mar_b_n">
		<a href="/wgbh/nova/thin/"><b>Dying to be Thin</b></a></p>
		<p class="caption">
		Life-threatening eating disorders such as anorexia and bulimia are on the rise. Here you can watch the entire NOVA program in QuickTime or RealPlayer, read expert advice and the personal experiences of sufferers, access valuable resources, find out what your body's nutritional needs are, and more.</p></td>
	</tr>
		<tr>
		<td colspan="2" align="center">
