		<td width="94" valign="top" align="left"><a href="/wgbh/nova/einstein/"><img src="/wgbh/nova/images02/icon_2311_einstein.jpg" alt="Einstein Revealed" width="80" height="61" border="0" hspace="0" vspace="0" /></a></td>
		<td valign="top"><p class="mar_b_n">
		<a href="/wgbh/nova/einstein/"><b>Einstein Revealed</b></a></p>
		<p class="caption">Review
the key turning points in Einstein's life, find out why he is considered a
genius among geniuses, become a "time traveler," learn how the theory of
general relativity gave birth to cosmology, and explore the nature of light.</p></td>
	</tr>
		<tr>
		<td colspan="2" align="center">
		<img src="/wgbh/nova/images02/spacer.gif" alt="" align="top" width="1" height="20" border="0" />
