  	<tr>
		<td width="94" valign="top" align="left"><a href="/wgbh/nova/egypt/"><img src="/wgbh/nova/images02/icon_0000_egypt.jpg" alt="Mysteries of the Nile" width="80" height="61" border="0" hspace="0" vspace="0" /></a></td>
		<td valign="top"><p class="mar_b_n">
  		<a href="/wgbh/nova/egypt/"><b>Mysteries of the Nile</b></a></p>
		<p class="caption">
		Explore
the Pyramids, temples, and other monumental architecture of ancient Egypt
through riveting 360&#176; photography and field dispatches from noted
Egyptologists. Then, see what it takes to try to raise a giant granite obelisk
using only the tools and techniques of the ancients.</p></td>
	</tr>
