		<td width="94" valign="top" align="left"><a href="/wgbh/nova/shackleton/"><img src="/wgbh/nova/images02/icon_2906_shacklet.jpg" alt="Shackleton's Antarctic Odyssey" width="80" height="61" border="0" hspace="0" vspace="0" /></a></td>
		<td valign="top"><p class="mar_b_n">
		<a href="/wgbh/nova/shackleton/"><b>Shackleton's Voyage of Endurance</b></a></p>
		<p class="caption">
Journey
into ice-choked Antarctic waters and onto the shores of rugged Elephant and
South Georgia islands as you follow in the footsteps of Sir Ernest Shackleton,
whose legendary 1914-1916 <i>Endurance</i> expedition is one of the greatest
survival stories of all time.</p></td>
	</tr>
