		<td valign="top"><p class="mar_b_n">
  		<a href="/wgbh/nova/tothemoon/"><b>To the Moon</b></a></p>
		<p class="caption">
		Join
the Apollo astronauts on the moon's surface through stunning 360&#176;
photography, find out why scientists believe the moon used to be part of the
Earth, give your brain a workout with some lunar puzzlers, and hear from the
space pioneers, including the last man to walk on the moon.</p></td>
